  Locus:
    Page: 59
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Children
---
What is a child? An experiment. A fresh attempt to produce the just man.
...that is to make humanity divine. ...And if you should try to shape this
new being in your idea of a godly man or a godly woman, you will destroy
its own holiest expectation and perhaps create a monster.
